name: Trippin with Kintha
description:
Kintha is a naughty girl from another dimension.
She loves 3D matrix, people, love, tarot readings and having fun.
And Jenny is a young woman living in Morocco who loves to explore the world and the universe.

Jenny met Kintha on one of her astral travels and after that they shared all their wisdom. They are now best friends and having lots of fun.
